kabhi teri yaado me mashroof rehne ko dil karta hai
kabhi teri saanso ko mehsoos karne ko dil karta hai
ye mere mohabbat ki bebasi hai
ke is dil ko bhi hamesha tere paas rehne ko dil karta hai
